    <title>hexo中常见的命令</title>
    <link href="https://lassksy.github.io/2022/08/09/hexo%E4%B8%AD%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E7%9A%84%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4/"/>
    <id>https://lassksy.github.io/2022/08/09/hexo%E4%B8%AD%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E7%9A%84%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4/</id>
    <published>2022-08-09T12:06:30.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-08-09T12:29:00.668Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="HEXO中几个常见的命令"><a href="#HEXO中几个常见的命令" class="headerlink" title="HEXO中几个常见的命令"></a>HEXO中几个常见的命令</h2><p>本文将介绍几个hexo常用常见的几个指令。</p><h3 id="1-init"><a href="#1-init" class="headerlink" title="1.init"></a>1.init</h3><p>新建一个网站，如果没有<code>folder</code>,Hexo默认在当前文件夹建立网站</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init [folder]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-new"><a href="#2-new" class="headerlink" title="2.new"></a>2.new</h3><p>新建一篇文章。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new [layout] &lt;title&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><table><thead><tr><th>指令</th><th>描述</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>-p</code>, <code>--path</code></td><td>自定义新文章的路径</td></tr><tr><td><code>r</code>, <code>--replace</code></td><td>如果存在同名文章，将其替换</td></tr><tr><td><code>s</code>, <code>--slug</code></td><td>文章的Slug，作为新文章的文件名和发布后的URL</td></tr></tbody></table><h3 id="3-generate"><a href="#3-generate" class="headerlink" title="3.generate"></a>3.generate</h3><p>生成本地静态文件。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo generate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>可简写为：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="4-publish"><a href="#4-publish" class="headerlink" title="4.publish"></a>4.publish</h3><p>发表草稿。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo pubish [layout] &lt;filename&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="5-server"><a href="#5-server" class="headerlink" title="5.server"></a>5.server</h3><p>启动本地服务器，默认访问地址为<a class="link" href="http://localhost:4000/">http://localhost:4000/<i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></a></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>可简写为：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="6-deploy"><a href="#6-deploy" class="headerlink" title="6.deploy"></a>6.deploy</h3><p>部署网站到服务器。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>可简写为</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="7-clean"><a href="#7-clean" class="headerlink" title="7.clean"></a>7.clean</h3><p>清除缓存文件（<code>db.json</code>）和静态文件（<code>public</code>）。<br>在某些情况（尤其是更换主题后），如果发现您对站点的更改无论如何也不生效，您可能需要运行该命令。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="资料来源https-hexo-io-zh-cn-docs-commands"><a href="#资料来源https-hexo-io-zh-cn-docs-commands" class="headerlink" title="资料来源https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/commands"></a>资料来源<a class="link" href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/commands">https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/commands<i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></a></h2>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
