  <entry>
    <title>Linux下使用hexo搭建博客</title>
    <link href="https://lassksy.github.io/2022/08/09/Linux%E4%B8%8B%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/"/>
    <id>https://lassksy.github.io/2022/08/09/Linux%E4%B8%8B%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/</id>
    <published>2022-08-09T05:57:30.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-08-09T12:56:57.874Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>本文将介绍如何在linux下利用 <code>hexo</code> +<code>Github Pages</code> 搭建一个简单的个人博客，内容包括<code>Git</code>,<code>Node.js</code>的安装及其使用，以及在搭建博客时碰见的问题以及解决方法。</p><h2 id="1-Git的下载安装"><a href="#1-Git的下载安装" class="headerlink" title="1.Git的下载安装"></a>1.<strong>Git</strong>的下载安装</h2><pre><code>安装Git在终端输入<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">apt-get install git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>安装完成后可以输入git --version验证是否安装成功（如输出版本号则为安装成功）</code></pre><p><img lazyload src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="https://tva3.sinaimg.cn/large/0083CpMNgy1h50hsu33stj30me0gnjsk.jpg" alt="gitverson"></p><h2 id="2-Node-js的下载安装"><a href="#2-Node-js的下载安装" class="headerlink" title="2.Node.js的下载安装"></a>2.<strong>Node.js</strong>的下载安装</h2><pre><code>使用snap进行安装在终端输入<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo snap install node --classic</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>-官网下载安装进入node的官网 &lt;https://nodejs.org/zh-cn/&gt;点击长期维护版本</code></pre><p><img lazyload src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="https://tva2.sinaimg.cn/large/0083CpMNgy1h50iqmg1mzj31ct0ujk8a.jpg" alt="nodejs01"><br>    解压文件<br>    <figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">tar -xvf node-v16.16.0-linux-x64.tar.xz</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>    进入目录<br>    <figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd node-v16.16.0-linux-x64/bin</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>    验证是否安装成功<br>    <figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">node -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br><img lazyload src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/0083CpMNgy1h50ih6rgw0j30me0gnab2.jpg" alt="nodejs02"></p><h2 id="3-安装hexo"><a href="#3-安装hexo" class="headerlink" title="3.安装hexo"></a>3.安装hexo</h2><p>git和node.js安装完成后，即可使用npm安装Hexo。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g hexo-cli</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>安装完成后，执行以下命令，Hexo将会在指定文件夹中新建所需文件。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init &lt;你自己的博客文件夹&gt;</span><br><span class="line">cd &lt;你自己的博客文件夹&gt;</span><br><span class="line">npm install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img lazyload src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="https://tva4.sinaimg.cn/large/0083CpMNgy1h50lnd8z9wj30me0gnn62.jpg" alt="hexoinstall"><br>生成<strong>静态文件</strong>到默认设置的<code>public</code>文件夹。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>启动本地服务器，用于预览主题。默认地址：<a class="link" href="http://localhost:4000/">http://localhost:4000/<i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></a></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img lazyload src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/0083CpMNgy1h50lt7u6p1j30me0gnqcc.jpg" alt="hexos"><br>打开<a class="link" href="http://localhost:4000/">http://localhost:4000<i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></a><br><img lazyload src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/0083CpMNgy1h50lue8uzxj31cv0rcqkx.jpg" alt="4000"><br>至此，博客的本地静态文件生成完毕。</p><h2 id="4-为博客安装主题"><a href="#4-为博客安装主题" class="headerlink" title="4.为博客安装主题"></a>4.为博客安装主题</h2><p>打开<code>hexo-theme</code><a class="link" href="https://hexo.io/themes/">https://hexo.io/themes/<i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></a><br>选择自己喜欢的主题，然后根据主题使用手册指引安装主题到<code>themes</code>文件夹<br><em><strong>以keep主题为例</strong></em></p><h3 id="安装"><a href="#安装" class="headerlink" title="安装"></a>安装</h3><p><del>如果使用 Hexo 5.0 或更高版本，最简单的安装方式是通过 npm：<br>打开博客所在文件夹进入其终端，键入</del><br>已失效</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-theme-keep</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>或者使用<code>git</code>clone整个keep主题仓库：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git clone https://github.com/XPoet/hexo-theme-keep themes/keep</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img lazyload src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/0083CpMNgy1h50maevxd4j30me0gnqbh.jpg" alt="keppinstall"></p><h3 id="使用"><a href="#使用" class="headerlink" title="使用"></a>使用</h3><p>安装完成后打开hexo配置文件<code>_config.yml</code> 将<code>theme</code>设置为<code>keep</code></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">theme: keep</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img lazyload src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="https://tva2.sinaimg.cn/large/0083CpMNgy1h50mcib81rj31560n9k2k.jpg" alt="keeptheme"><br>终端输入</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果更改之后碰见主题还是默认的情况，将<code>themes</code>文件夹中的<code>keep</code>文件夹删除后重新再终端输入</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git clone https://github.com/XPoet/hexo-theme-keep themes/keep</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>问题解决<br><img lazyload src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/0083CpMNgy1h50moimasbj31ct0rndl1.jpg" alt="keepsite"></p><h3 id="自定义"><a href="#自定义" class="headerlink" title="自定义"></a>自定义</h3><p>参考keep官方主题使用手册指引<a class="link" href="https://keep-docs.xpoet.cn/usage-tutorial/configuration-guide.html#base-info">https://keep-docs.xpoet.cn/usage-tutorial/configuration-guide.html#base-info<i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></a></p><h2 id="部署博客到github上"><a href="#部署博客到github上" class="headerlink" title="部署博客到github上"></a>部署博客到github上</h2><p><a class="link" href="https://github.com/signup?ref_cta=Sign+up&ref_loc=header+logged+out&ref_page=/&source=header-home">注册<i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></a>或<a class="link" href="https://github.com/login?return_to=https://github.com/signup?ref_cta=Sign+up&ref_loc=header+logged+out&ref_page=%252F&source=header-home">登陆<i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></a>github账号</p><p>新建一个<code>Repositories</code>，并命名为&lt;你的github账号名字&gt;.github.io<br><img lazyload src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/0083CpMNgy1h50myh6kxij315y0q247u.jpg" alt="github"></p><h3 id="安装hexo-deployer-git"><a href="#安装hexo-deployer-git" class="headerlink" title="安装hexo-deployer-git"></a>安装hexo-deployer-git</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>修改根目录下的<code>_config.yml</code>文件，配置github相关信息：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">  type: git</span><br><span class="line">  repo: git@github.com:qaqmal/qaqmal.github.io.git</span><br><span class="line">  brach: main</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>设置user.name和user.email配置信息：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global user.name &quot;你的GitHub用户名&quot;</span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.email &quot;你的GitHub注册邮箱&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>生成ssh密钥文件：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C &quot;你的GitHub注册邮箱&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后直接三个回车即可，默认不需要设置密码<br>然后找到生成的.ssh的文件夹中的id_rsa.pub密钥，将内容全部复制<br>打开<a class="link" href="https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https://github.com/settings/keys">GitHub_Settings_keys<i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></a> 页面，新建new SSH Key</p><p>Title为标题，任意填即可，将刚刚复制的id_rsa.pub内容粘贴进去，最后点击Add SSH key。</p><p>  部署到GitHub</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="结语"><a href="#结语" class="headerlink" title="结语"></a>结语</h2><p>至此，个人博客就搭建完成了,可以访问<code>&lt;你的用户名&gt;.github.io</code>查看网页。</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
